{"tid":2185362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中国又贏】李孝利慘遭強國網民咒死 今宣佈3天後關IG","createTime":"2020-09-02T08:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T11:24:58.000Z","uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c42da630986578835a5eb225fa34f121baf35447","tid":2185362,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200902/LOT4WSQLAFBQJGVFLR2DNDXOFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200902%2FLOT4WSQLAFBQJGVFLR2DNDXOFQ%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=b2faccba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200902%2FLOT4WSQLAFBQJGVFLR2DNDXOFQ%2F&h=d4d6e3c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200902/LOT4WSQLAFBQJGVFLR2DNDXOFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國性感歌姬李孝利近日為MBC節目《玩什麼好呢？》再組限定組合，孖嚴正花、華莎及Jessi組成限定女團「退貨遠征隊」，「國民MC」劉在錫就擔任經理人。李孝利於上月22日播出的節目中，就提到想用「Mao（毛的讀音）」作藝名而惹大陸網民不滿，指李孝利用中共已故領導人毛澤東的姓氏開玩笑，有辱華之嫌。雖然之後節目組方面已強調當中有誤會，亦將藝名改成「千玉」，但李孝利卻依舊受到大陸網民狙擊，令昨日與老友李尚順結婚7周年的李孝利宣佈3天後將停用IG賬號。<br />\n<br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hyoleehyolee/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhyoleehyolee%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=88993ae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hyoleehyolee/</a>"},{"pid":"0f1c8c3b56c3e6c354af82ef08f83fd64702ec55","tid":2185362,"uid":198503,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"等睇韓國排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a754d9e63f8b94b823b95c921e0e6c694797c9","tid":2185362,"uid":333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"班韓國fans有咩反應同行動"},{"pid":"1c0e52c11e739d53f3c9603309ff9a8384a4cdfa","tid":2185362,"uid":141442,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0